rom <code>None</code> or <code>Receive</code> to <code>Send</code> or <code>SendReceive</code> , and if the attendee turned on their video or content streams, remote attendees can receive those streams, but only after media renegotiation between the client and the Amazon Chime back-end server.</p> </li>
